OL,3,CPolice warn against fireworks at
OL,4,Cweekend Iran war protests
OL,6,FFireworks will not be tolerated at
OL,7,FIran war protests in London this
OL,8,Fweekend, police have warned after they
OL,9,Fwere used at recent demonstrations.
OL,11,FThe Metropolitan Police said it has
OL,12,Fimposed a number of conditions ahead
OL,13,Fof this weekend's protests against the
OL,14,Fstrikes on Iran and the Iranian
OL,15,Fgovernment "to minimise disruption to
OL,16,Fothers".
OL,26,@wD@LOUxD@GO]
