OL,3,CPolice warn against fireworks at
OL,4,Cweekend Iran war protests
OL,6,FOn Saturday afternoon, a Stop the War
OL,7,Fdemonstration against the US and
OL,8,FIsraeli strikes on Iran will march
OL,9,Ffrom Russell Square near the British
OL,10,FMuseum to Richmond Terrace, Whitehall,
OL,11,Fwhere speeches will take place.
OL,13,FThe Met said the assembly in Richmond
OL,14,FTerrace must finish at 6pm and any
OL,15,Fspeeches and amplified music must stop
OL,16,Fat 5.30pm.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
