CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1774260876
OL,3,CPolice warn against fireworks at
OL,4,Cweekend Iran war protests
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a separate Stage for
OL,7,FFreedom demonstration against the
OL,8,FIranian government will march from
OL,9,FHyde Park Corner in Knightsbridge to
OL,10,Fthe Iranian embassy near Hyde Park.
OL,12,FThe force said the assembly at the
OL,13,Fembassy must conclude at 5pm.
OL,15,FScotland Yard added it has banned the
OL,16,Fuse of amplified sound equipment for
OL,17,Fmusic or speech, or any other item to
OL,18,Fcreate noise, including musical
OL,19,Finstruments, soundemitting devices,
OL,20,For items struck or banged together.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
