PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1774260876
OL,3,CPolice warn against fireworks at
OL,4,Cweekend Iran war protests
OL,6,FSuperintendent Neil Holyoak, who is in
OL,7,Fcharge of policing London this
OL,8,Fweekend, said: "Officers will be on
OL,9,Fduty this weekend to police these
OL,10,Fevents and ensure they pass off safely
OL,11,Fand peacefully. As always, we will not
OL,12,Fhesitate to act if we see criminality.
OL,14,F"We have imposed conditions, chiefly
OL,15,Fto minimise noise and disruption to
OL,16,Flocal residents based on extensive
OL,17,Ffeedback. Those who refuse to comply
OL,18,Fwith the conditions risk being
OL,19,Farrested.
OL,26,@pD@POUvD@AOU
