CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1774260876
OL,3,CPolice warn against fireworks at
OL,4,Cweekend Iran war protests
OL,6,F"We will also not tolerate people
OL,7,Fsetting off fireworks which we have
OL,8,Fseen in recent weeks.
OL,10,F"Please ensure if you are planning to
OL,11,Fattend this weekend's events you act
OL,12,Fwithin the law and respect surrounding
OL,13,Fresidents and businesses."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@ZO]
